{"tid":1978944,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［買枕頭］有冇頸椎有問題嘅巴絲？","createTime":"2020-04-19T05:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T13:36:38.000Z","uid":167426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2e250254a5346394bcf593f659109f40b6fcfa6c","tid":1978944,"uid":167426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:34:32.000Z","msg":"自己條頸好似有啲過直，仲有其他問題<br />\n最近情況差咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瞓屋企嗰枕瞓到好唔舒服<br />\n我見好多人推介tempur<br />\n我應該買tempur嗰個立體健頸枕定健康弧度枕？<br />\n見有啲巴絲分享話用完條頸情況好咗好多<br />\n不過唔知佢地買邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fabecfecf6102361b6a7621ffe9fbd21ca297c","tid":1978944,"uid":167426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"另外，有冇醫生推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中，西醫，物理治療都睇過，冇乜好轉<br />\n中醫淨係識啪頸，西醫同物理治療都好似冇乜用"},{"pid":"c7ba5a5a9da6567f260f75f9a10e6ae35710949e","tid":1978944,"uid":167426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed36eb746072b530238e2730455c9852a1ab578","tid":1978944,"uid":44346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"有無照X光<br />\n枕頭要試架<br />\n<br />\n我自己頸椎都有事<br />\n反而日日伸展拉筋（用埋花生球）<br />\n返辦公室長期提住自己收下巴<br />\n個mon放返啱嘅位，唔好成日睇手機<br />\n咁好快有改善"},{"pid":"030fc82f80c236f5854f4c22735f9ac443b47f92","tid":1978944,"uid":167426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ed36eb746072b530238e2730455c9852a1ab578","tid":1978944,"uid":44346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"有無照X光<br />\n枕頭要試架<br />\n<br />\n我自己頸椎都有事<br />\n反而日日伸展拉筋（用埋花生球）<br />\n返辦公室長期提住自己收下巴<br />\n個mon放返啱嘅位，唔好成日睇手機<br />\n咁好快有改善"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:44:35.000Z","msg":"有啊<br />\n就係照完話我過直<br />\n其實自己已經試過嗰個立體健頸枕<br />\n係幾舒服<img src=\"/a